{"id":288736,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-四川三台县15访民在北京被跟踪并受到威胁/","date":"2013-04-11T19:32:08Z","modified":"2013-04-11T19:32:08Z","title":"维权网 | 四川三台县15访民在北京被跟踪并受到威胁（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>      （维权网信息员陈华报道）四川省三台县景福镇蜜蜂嘴村五组的陈小青，</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>，向派出所递交到北京旅游的告知书后，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>与吴吉伟、龙保军、赵德玉、冯中富、邓前银、羊衍伦、肖方礼、刘志琼、林俊生、唐有合、曾怀宪、羊衍全、左王庆、邓前银等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>人，乘坐火车到北京旅游。</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></b></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>上午，在向国家信访局递交了各自的上访材料后，被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多人跟踪。从公交车一直跟到地铁站。</span><span> </span><span>跟踪的人对陈小青等人说：“没办法，我们也是受人之托，必须跟踪你们，在一定情况下，就会对你们下手。”﹙有录音﹚。惊恐之下，陈小青等人只有跑到马家楼救助站，但跟踪的人一直在外面守候。陈小青请求社会关注。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，陈小青随旅行团到北京旅游，被作为非法上访人员，被景福镇派出所李伟才强行从北京遣返回家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈小青是因为到场镇赶场看热闹，被无端带到派出所关押、拘禁，并抢走身上钱物至今不予归还而上访的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈小青电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 15386659499</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-oqaqAKX4FRw/UWbrFr2e7GI/AAAAAAAAgOU/lFnuKHDlFZc/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130412005419.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-oqaqAKX4FRw/UWbrFr2e7GI/AAAAAAAAgOU/lFnuKHDlFZc/s400/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130412005419.png\" width=\"296\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</